    "movements within typical technological limits (between 200-1000 milliseconds).",
    "On the other days, patients randomly exposed to the 3 sec-delay, 5 sec-delay, or 7 sec-delay synchrony conditions: the SIA synchronizes with the patient's movements after a delay of 3, 5, or 7 sec.",
